%20answer%20is%3A%20not%20anymore%2C%26quot%3B%20Bailey%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20the%20reason%20being%20is%2C%20I%20think%20I%20told%20some%20of%20you%20guys%20that%20when%20I%20was%20pregnant%2C%20I%20had%20just%2C%20like%2C%20started%20craving%20meat.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20her%20pregnancy%20cravings%20for%20meat%2C%20she%20had%20been%20vegan%20for%20about%2013%20years%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20just%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BWell%2C%20I'm%20gonna%20give%20my%20body%20what%20it%20wants%20right%20now%20because%20I'm%20doing%20a%20really%20hard%20job%20of%20growing%20a%20human%2C%20and%20I%20also%20wanted%20to%20make%20sure%20Halo%20was%20getting%20the%20proper%20nutrients%20and%20things%20he%20needed%2C%26quot%3B%20Bailey%20said.%20She%20welcomed%20her%20son%2C%20Halo%2C%20with%20her%20partner%2C%20DDG%2C%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20singer%20shared%20that%20even%20though%20she%20started%20consuming%20meat%2C%20she%20still%20eats%20mostly%20vegan%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20have%20an%20inkling%20or%20craving%20for%20chicken%20or%20something%2C%20I'll%20eat%20it.%20But%20I%20don't%20eat%20a%20lot%20of%20meat.%20But%20it's%20like%20if%20I%20want%20it%2C%20I'm%20going%20to%20have%20it%2C%20and%20then%20that's%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Bailey%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20she%20eventually%20learned%20that%20it%20wasn't%20that%20unusual%20for%20vegans%20to%20change%20their%20diet%20while%20pregnant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20looking%20it%20up%20and%20I%20see%20so%20many%20women%20like%20me%20who%20were%20vegan%20for%20years%20and%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Bailey%20said.%20%26quot%3BOnce%20they%20got%20pregnant%2C%20it%20was%2C%20like%2C%20out%20the%20window.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDr.%20Allison%20Suttle%2C%20a%20gynecologist%20and%20chief%20medical%20officer%20at%20Sanford%20Health%2C%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20meat%20cravings%20can%20be%20a%20sign%20that%20the%20body%2