0Ghatage%20was%20in%20his%20first%20year%20of%20a%20master's%20degree%20when%20he%20came%20up%20with%20a%20unique%20strategy%20to%20make%20the%20most%20of%20a%20university%20career%20fair.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20only%20been%20at%20Carnegie%20Mellon%20University%20for%20three%20months%20and%20knew%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmetaverse-job-fair-avatar-creepy-careers-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecareer%20fair%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20not%20meant%20for%20non-graduating%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20he%20created%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fresume-tips-google-software-engineer-skills-experience-careers-software-tech-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecustom%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20each%20employer.%20While%20the%20text%20remained%20the%20same%2C%20each%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20included%20a%20unique%20QR%20code%20that%20led%20to%20his%20personal%20portfolio%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20was%20to%20give%20them%20out%20and%20then%20track%20which%20recruiters%20took%20enough%20interest%20in%20his%20profile%20to%20scan%20the%20code.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20just%20handing%20out%20resumes%20and%20seeing%20who%20was%20actually%20hitting%20me%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20Ghatage%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20time%20came%20after%20nine%20months%20for%20my%20actual%20career%20fair%2C%20I%20focused%20on%20those%20companies%20a%20bit%20more.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20doubled%20down%20on%20custom%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20and%20talked%20to%20recruiters%20at%20those%20companies%20instead%20of%20only%20visiting%20marquee%20names%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-write-big-tech-resume-google-meta-product-manager-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20and%20Meta%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffinding-job-awful-right-now-drop-in-openings-tough-search-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elong%20queues%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20really%20helped%20because%20right%20out%20of%20the%20first%20career%20fair%20I%20attended%20properly%2C%20I%20had%20six%20or%20seven%20calls%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECisco%2C%20where%20Ghatage%20landed%20a%20full-time%20offer%2C%20was%20one%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20next%20three%20years%2C%20he%20worked%20at%20Cisco%20and%20SAP.%20In%202019%2C%20he%20moved%20over%20to%20Salesforce%2C%20where%20he%20is%20currently%20a%20software%20engineer%20at%20the%20company's%20Bay%20Area%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20that%20Ghatage%20used%20to%20attend%20job%20fairs%20in%202016%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221124%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22image%20of%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20of%20tech%20employee%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e6ee7cd17aa3c7b2b2b1df%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221454%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGhatage's%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20in%202016%20during%20his%20master's%20program.%3Cp%3EAnup%20Ghatage%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%20on%20the%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20he%20created%20eight%20years%20ago%2C%20there%20are%20three%20things%20Ghatage%20would%20keep%20the%20same%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOne%20page%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Now%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20interview%20panels%2C%20Ghatage%20recommends%20sticking%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-write-big-tech-resume-google-meta-product-manager-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone-page%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20even%20if%20it%20means%20trimming%20down%20the%20skills%20and%20education%20sections.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHonestly%2C%20interviewing%20is%20a%20very%20boring%20job%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20and%20most%20technical%20reviewers%20want%20to%20get%20back%20to%20their%20more%20urgent