20document%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOpen%20source%20contributions%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Projects%20on%20open%20source%20communities%20like%20Apache%20have%20been%20a%20career%20boost%20for%20Ghatage%20since%20he%20started%20working%20on%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOpen%20source%20contributions%20are%20akin%20to%20actual%20job%20experience%20which%20is%20validated%20by%20industry%20experts%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20about%20adding%20them%20below%20his%20education%20details.%20%26quot%3BThis%20would%20serve%20as%20a%20great%20signal%20to%20potential%20employers%20that%20my%20knowledge%20and%20skills%20have%20been%20peer%20reviewed%20by%20industry%20experts%20and%20are%20already%20making%20impact.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETweaking%20work%20experience%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Writing%20about%20early%20work%20experience%20is%20tough%20because%20it%20often%20had%20limited%20impact%2C%20Ghatage%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20perhaps%20research%20more%20about%20how%20it%20is%20more%20relevant%20to%20the%20jobs%20that%20I'm%20applying%20to.%26quot%3B%20He%20also%20said%20he%20would%20move%20work%20experience%20above%20the%20skills%20section%20since%20it%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20bigger%20value%20add.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20has%20verified%20his%20work%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20work%20in%20tech%2C%20consulting%2C%20or%20finance%20and%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20your%20personal%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20journey%3F%20Please%20reach%20out%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ashubhangigoel%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eshubhangigoel%40insider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsalesforce-engineer-shares-resume-hack-that-helped-land-first-job-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%