ng%20from%20semiconductors%20to%20electronics%20to%20biotechnology%2C%20where%20they%20discussed%20the%20potential%20and%20opportunities%20India%20has%20to%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20those%20who%20took%20part%20at%20the%20CEO%20roundtable%20were%20Chairman%20President%20and%20CEO%20Adobe%20Shantanu%20Narayen%3B%20CEO%20Google%20Sundar%20Pichai%3B%20CEO%20IBM%20Arvind%20Krishna%3B%20Lisa%20Su-Chair%20and%20CEO%20AMD%3B%20Noubar%20Afeyan-Chairman%20Moderna.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20CEOs%20of%20leading%20US-based%20companies%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20was%20to%20discuss%20fostering%20greater%20collaborations%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20in%20the%20cutting-edge%20areas%20of%20AI%2C%20quantum%20computing%2C%20semiconductors%2C%20and%20biotechnology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20India%20US%20bilateral%20meeting%20on%20Saturday%2C%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20praised%20combined%20efforts%20to%20facilitate%20resilient%2C%20secure%2C%20and%20sustainable%20semiconductor%20supply%20chains%20including%20through%20GlobalFoundries'%20(GF)%20creation%20of%20the%20GF%20Kolkata%20Power%20Center%20in%20Kolkata%2C%20India%20that%20will%20enhance%20mutually%20beneficial%20linkages%20in%20research%20and%20development%20in%20chip%20manufacturing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20joint%20fact%20sheet%20released%20by%20the%20White%20House%2C%20the%20leaders%20welcomed%20new%20private%20sector%20cooperation%20on%20emerging%20technologies%2C%20such%20as%20through%20IBM's%20recent%20conclusion%20of%20memoranda%20of%20understanding%20with%20the%20Indian%20government%2C%20which%20will%20enable%20IBM's%20Watsonx%20platform%20on%20India's%20Airawat%20supercomputer%20and%20drive%20new%20AI%20innovation%20opportunities%2C%20enhance%20R%26amp%3BD%20collaboration%20on%20advanced%20semiconductor%20processors%2C%20and%20increase%20support%20for%20India's%20National%20Quantum%20Mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20the%20leaders%20welcomed%20progress%20since%20the%20November%202023%20signing%20of%20an%20MoU%20between%20the%20Commerce%20Department%20and%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Commerce%20and%20Industry%20to%20enhance%20the%20two%20countries'%20innovation%20ecosystems%20under%20the%20%26quot%3BInnovation%20Handshake%26quot%3B%20agenda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20the%20two%20sides%20have%20convened%20two%20industry%20roundtables%20in%20the%20US%20and%20India%20to%20bring%20together%20startups%2C%20private%20equity%20and%20venture%20capital%20firms%2C%20corporate%20investment%20departments%2C%20and%20government%20officials%20to%20forge%20connections%20and%20to%20accelerate%20investment%20in%20innovation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20in%20New%20York%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20on%20Sunday%20also%20addressed%20a%20huge%20gathering%20of%20the%20Indian%20community%20who%20converged%20in%20thousands%20from%20various%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Day%201%2C%20Saturday%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20took%20part%20in%20the%20fourth%20Quad%20Leaders'%20Summit%20in%20Wilmington%2C%20Delaware%2C%20which%20is%20being%20hosted%20by%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden.%20Following%20the%20request%20of%20the%20US%20side%20to%20host%20the%20Quad%20Summit%20this%20year%2C%20India%20has%20agreed%20to%20host%20the%20next%20Quad%20Summit%20in%202025.%20The%20forum%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20key%20group%20of%20the%20like-minded%20countries%20to%20work%20for%20peace%2C%20progress%20and%20prosperity%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Day%203%2C%20Monday%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20will%20address%20the%20'Summit%20of%20the%20Future'%20at%20the%20United%20Nations%20General%20Assembly%20in%20New%20York%2C%20before%20he%20departs%20for%20India.%20The%20theme%20of%20the%20Summit%20is%20'Multilateral%20Solutions%20for%20a%20Better%20Tomorrow'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20large%20number%20of%20global%20leaders%20are%20expected%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20