009a0fac852d5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223335%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPope%20Francis%20said%20in%20a%20meeting%20that%20universal%20basic%20income%20will%20be%20essential%20as%20AI%20takes%20more%20jobs.%3Cp%3EVatican%20Pool%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EPope%20Francis%20has%20become%20a%20vocal%20advocate%20for%20a%20universal%20basic%20income.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20first%20staked%20his%20position%20in%20a%20letter%20in%202020%2C%20calling%20UBI%20critical%20to%20the%20future%20economy.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIn%20a%20meeting%20on%20Friday%2C%20the%20Pope%20again%20called%20for%20a%20basic%20income.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20the%20figurehead%20you'd%20expect%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funiversal-basic-income-ubi%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Euniversal%20basic%20income%3C%2Fa%3E%20movement%2C%20which%20is%20mostly%20driven%20by%20tech%20CEOs%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%20but%20it's%20the%20one%20with%20by%20far%20the%20most%20followers%3A%20Pope%20Francis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPope%20Francis%20has%20advocated%20for%20a%20universal%20basic%20income%2C%20or%20UBI%2C%20for%20several%20years.%20He%20first%20announced%20his%20support%20in%202020%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpope-francis-it-might-be-time-to-consider-universal-basic-wage-2020-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehe%20wrote%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20leaders%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20prominent%20social%20movements%20that%20it%20%26quot%3Bmay%20be%20the%20time%20to%20consider%20a%20universal%20basic%20wage%20which%20would%20acknowledge%20and%20dignify%20the%20noble%2C%20essential%20tasks%20you%20carry%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20would%20ensure%20and%20concretely%20achieve%20the%20ideal%2C%20at%20once%20so%20human%20and%20so%20Christian%2C%20of%20no%20worker%20without%20rights%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Pope%20said%20in%20that%20letter%20that%20some%20of%20the%20lowest%20class%20members%20of%20society%20%26quot%3Bhave%20been%20excluded%20from%20the%20benefits%20of%20globalization%26quot%3B%20and%20often%20slip%20through%20the%20cracks%20of%20existing%20labor%20protections.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn't%20a%20passing%20thought.%20Pope%20Francis%20continues%20to%20talk%20about%20it%2C%20most%20recently%20on%20Friday%20during%20a%20meeting%20with%20members%20of%20Popular%20Movements%20%E2%80%94%20a%20group%20of%20leaders%20of%20grassroots%20organizations%20from%20five%20continents.%20The%20Pope%20told%20them%20that%20UBI%2C%20in%20the%20age%20of%20AI%20and%20automation%2C%20should%20not%20just%20be%20considered%20%26quot%3Bcompassion%26quot%3B%20but%20%26quot%3Bstrict%20justice%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20The%20Vatican.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20basic%20income%20%E2%80%94%20recurring%2C%20unconditional%20payments%20%E2%80%94%20falls%20into%20two%20categories%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funiversal-basic-income-ubi%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Euniversal%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhich-states-cities-have-guaranteed-basic-income-programs-low-income-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eguaranteed%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20latter%20targets%20specific%20groups%20of%20people%2C%20usually%20low-income%20or%20other%20vulnerable%20communities.%20A%20universal%20basic%20income%20would%20go%20to%20all%20citizens%2C%20regardless%20of%20their%20economic%20status.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20programs%20allow%20recipients%20to%20spend%20the%20money%20however%20they%20want.%20That's%20different%20than%20government%20assistance%20programs%20like%20SNAP%2C%20which%20forces%20recipients%20to%20use%20the%20cash%20on%20things%20like%20food%20and%20healthcare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20basic%20income%20is%20popular%20among%20the%20Silicon%20Valley%20crowd%2C%20which%20believes%20many%20people%20could%20lose%20their%20jobs%20to%20AI%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlmost%2012%20million%20Americans%20in%20jobs%20with%20shrinking%20demand%20will%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjobs-at-risk-from-ai-replace-change-chatgpt-automation-study-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eto%20switch%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%202030%2C%20according%20to%20a%20McKinsey%20analysis%20published%20in%20July.%20Researchers%20said%20AI%20is%20a%20key%20reason%20for%20the%20shift%2C%20estimating%20that%2030%25%20of%20hours%20worked%20in%20the%20United%20States%20could%20be%20automated%20by%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Vatican%20did%20not%20immediately%20return%20a%20comment%20request%20from%20Business%20Insider%20about%20The%20Pope's%20support%20for%20UBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpope-francis-universal-basic-income-ai-jobs-automation-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727038561000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f07146d17aa3c7b2b4d65f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpope-francis-universal-basic-income-ai-jobs-automation-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pope%20Francis%20has%20for%20years%20called%20for%20a%20universal%20basic%20income%2C%20which%20he%20says%20will%20be%20crucial%20in%20the%20age%20of%20AI.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kniemeyer%40insider.com%20(Kenneth%20Niemeyer)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A558%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpope-francis-universal-basic-income-ai-jobs-automation-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BCould%20Not%20Die%20For%20Our%20Country%2C%20But%20Can%20Live%20For%20It%26quot%3B%3A%20PM%20Modi%20In%20New%20York%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20addressing%20thousands%20of%20expat%20Indians%20in%20New%20York%20today%