th%20the%20leadership%20of%20Sean%20O'Brien%2C%20the%20union's%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20very%20disappointed%20in%20Sean%20O'Brien's%20leadership%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20New%20York%20Democratic%20lawmaker%20told%20CNN's%20Manu%20Raju%20last%20week.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20found%20it%20increasingly%20alarming%20all%20year.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20Teamsters%20are%20in%20trouble%2C%20who%20do%20they%20call%20when%20we%20need%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20Teamsters%20pensions%20are%20bailed%20out%3F%20...%20It%20was%20Sean%20O'Brien%20calling%20Democrats%20for%20help%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOcasio-Cortez's%20remarks%20reveal%20just%20how%20much%20unions%20will%20matter%20in%20this%20election%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20with%20organizing%20and%20turnout%20efforts.%20And%20the%20consequential%20decision%20from%20the%20Teamsters%20has%20only%20heightened%20the%20efforts%20of%20both%20parties%20to%20make%20their%20case%20to%20rank-and-file%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224d85b5d1-4544-41c4-82a7-53d3384ac473%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Teamsters%20divide%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EO'Brien%20last%20week%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthehill.com%2Fhomenews%2Fcampaign%2F4887442-teamsters-union-endorsement-sean-obrien%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20The%20Hill%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20Teamsters%20won't%20back%20Harris%20or%20Trump%20because%20the%20union%20%26quot%3Bcouldn't%20get%20commitments%20on%20our%20issues%26quot%3B%20from%20either%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20CNN%20interview%2C%20O'Brien%20hit%20back%20at%20Ocasio-Cortez%2C%20saying%20the%20congresswoman%20%26quot%3Bshould%20maybe%20get%20into%20her%20district%20where%20it%20voted%20far-right%20Republican.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EO'Brien%20was%20referring%20to%20what%20he%20said%20were%20the%20results%20of%20union%20membership%20polling%20in%20her%2014th%20Congressional%20district%2C%20where%20he%20said%20members%20overwhelmingly%20backed%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Biden%20was%20still%20the%20presumptive%20Democratic%20nominee%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20he%20edged%20out%20Trump%20via%20in-person%20straw%20polls%20among%20members%20(44.3%25%20to%2036.3%25)%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fteamster.org%2F2024%2F09%2Fteamsters-release-presidential-endorsement-polling-data%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20Teamsters%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20in%20a%20national%20electronic%20poll%20that%20was%20open%20from%20from%20July%2024%20through%20September%2015%2C%20Trump%20held%20an%20advantage%20(59.6%25%20to%2034%25)%20over%20Harris%20among%20union%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20separate%20union%20survey%2C%20Trump%20also%20led%20Harris%20%E2%80%94%20this%20time%2058%25%20to%2031%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EO'Brien%20later%20said%20of%20Ocasio-Cortez%3A%20%26quot%3BShe%20may%20want%20to%20focus%20on%20her%20job%20instead%20of%20mine.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20O'Brien's%20CNN%20interview%2C%20Ocasio-Cortez%20responded%20to%20the%20union%20leader%2C%20arguing%20that%20Teamsters%20in%20her%20district%20were%20lined%20up%20behind%20Harris%20and%20her%20vice-presidential%20running%20mate%2C%20Minnesota%20Gov.%20Tim%20Walz.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20NY-14%20Teamsters%20mentioned%20here%20have%20actually%20voted%20overwhelmingly%20to%20endorse%20Harris-Walz.%20Just%20as%20Teamsters%20in%20Michigan%2C%20Nevada%2C%20and%20Pennsylvania%20have%2C%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FAOC%2Fstatus%2F1836816083858116716%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshe%20said%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20big%20thing%20to%20be%20wrong%20about.%20So%20let's%20set%20the%20record%20straight%3A%20Teamsters%20Local%20202%20are%20all%20in%20for%20Harris.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20congresswoman%20attached%20a%20letter%20from%20the%20New%20York%20City-based%20Teamsters%20Local%20Union%20No.%20202%2C%20which%20s