d.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20Summit%20of%20the%20Future%20on%20Saturday%2C%20where%20world%20leaders%20gathered%20at%20the%20UN%20headquarters%20in%20New%20York%20to%20discuss%20AI%20and%20other%20topics%2C%20Pichai%20made%20a%20powerful%20case%20for%20AI's%20benefits.%20He%20articulated%20four%20key%20areas%20where%20AI%20could%20further%20the%20UN's%20sustainable%20development%20goals%2C%2017%20goals%20that%20comprise%20a%20%26quot%3Bshared%20blueprint%20for%20peace%20and%20prosperity%20for%20people%20and%20the%20planet%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20UN.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2241abaed9-b170-4caf-ae54-7eb24e4c1792%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAccessing%20knowledge%20in%20their%20native%20language%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPichai%20said%20that%20over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20Google%20has%20added%20110%20new%20languages%20to%20Google%20Translate%20and%20is%20working%20toward%201%2C000%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20spoken%20languages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22938056f3-5582-4d3e-8f43-a092aa1c1d53%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAccelerating%20scientific%20discovery%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20May%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fblog.google%2Ftechnology%2Fai%2Fgoogle-deepmind-isomorphic-alphafold-3-ai-model%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20announced%20Alphafold%203%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20model%20developed%20by%20Google%20DeepMind%20and%20Isomorphic%20Labs%20that%20could%20accurately%20predict%20the%20structure%20of%20proteins%2C%20DNA%2C%20RNA%2C%20and%20ligands%2C%20and%20presented%20a%20novel%20breakthrough%20in%20drug%20discovery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20Google%20has%20made%20Alphafold%20free%20to%20use%2C%20and%20it%20has%20been%20accessed%20by%20over%202%20million%20researchers%20in%20over%20190%20countries%2C%2030%25%20of%20which%20are%20in%20the%20developing%20world%2C%20Pichai%20said.%20%26quot%3BGlobally%20Alphafold%20is%20being%20used%20in%20research%20that%20could%20help%20make%20crops%20more%20resistant%20to%20disease%2C%20discover%20new%20drugs%20in%20areas%20like%20malaria%20vaccines%2C%20and%20cancer%20treatments%2C%20and%20much%20more.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22881ef818-624e-4c07-818d-796a71b37c61%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMitigating%20climate%20disaster%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPichai%20said%20Google's%20Flood%20Hub%20system%20provides%20early%20warnings%20on%20climate%20disasters%20up%20to%20seven%20days%20in%20advance%20and%20protects%20over%20460%20million%20people%20in%2080%20countries.%20Google's%20boundary%20tracking%20systems%20for%20wildfires%20are%20also%20already%20in%2022%20countries.%20Earlier%20this%20month%2C%20Google%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fblog.google%2Foutreach-initiatives%2Fsustainability%2Fgoogle-ai-wildfire-detection%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%20FireSat%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%26quot%3Ba%20new%20global%20satellite%20constellation%20designed%20specifically%20to%20detect%20and%20track%20wildfires%20the%20size%20of%20a%20classroom%20within%2020%20minutes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20gives%20these%20technologies%20%26quot%3Ba%20boost%20in%20accuracy%2C%20speed%2C%20and%20scale%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227e290efd-42cc-4f9b-a8d5-cf7954bfce64%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EContributing%20to%20economic%20progress%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPichai%20said%20studies%20show%20that%20AI%20could%20boost%20global%20labor%20productivity%20by%201.4%20percentage%20points%20and%20increase%20global%20GDP%20by%207%20points%20within%20the%20next%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-ceo-sundar-pichai-un-summit-future-ai-advance-humanity-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727034584000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f071a3cfb7f307e573c551%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.c