%20proud%20of%20its%20children%20and%20makes%20the%20world%20realise%20that%20India%20is%20the%20world's%20'Vishwa-Bandhu'.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20our%20Indian%20values%20and%20culture%20that%20makes%20us%20One%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727028420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fvhcsshdo_prime-minister-narendra-modi_625x300_22_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcould-not-die-for-our-country-but-can-live-for-it-pm-narendra-modi-modi-in-new-york-6625930%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20addressing%20thousands%20of%20expat%20Indians%20in%20New%20York%20today%2C%20said%20as%20the%20first%20Prime%20Minister%20born%20after%20Independence%2C%20he%20could%20not%20give%20his%20life%20for%20the%20country%2C%20but%20he%20could%20certainly%20%26quot%3Blive%20for%20the%20country%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcould-not-die-for-our-country-but-can-live-for-it-pm-narendra-modi-modi-in-new-york-6625930%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BHave%20Very%20Ambitious%20Goals%20To%20Achieve%20In%203rd%20Term%26quot%3B%3A%20PM%20Modi%20In%20New%20York%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20Sunday%20said%20that%20he%20has%20set%20very%20ambitious%20goals%20in%20his%20third%20term%20to%20make%20the%20country%20a%20developed%20nation%20and%20asserted%20that%20India%20today%20is%20a%20land%20of%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20going%20through%20this%20tough%20election%20process%2C%20this%20long%20election%20system%2C%20something%20unprecedented%20happened%20in%20India%20(this%20year).%20What%20happened...%20%26quot%3BAbkibaar%20Modi%20Sarkaar%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said%20in%20his%20address%20to%20thousands%20of%20Indian%20Americans%20in%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20first%20time%20in%2060%20years%2C%20the%20people%20of%20India%20have%20given%20a%20mandate%20which%20has%20great%20significance.%20During%20my%20third%20term%2C%20I%20have%20very%20ambitious%20goals%20to%20achieve.%20We%20have%20to%20move%20forward%20with%20three%20times%20the%20strength%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20said%20he%20has%20dedicated%20his%20life%20for%20good%20governance%20and%20for%20a%20prosperous%20India.%20Observing%20that%20destiny%20brought%20him%20to%20politics%2C%20he%20said%20he%20had%20never%20thought%20of%20becoming%20a%20chief%20minister%20or%20prime%20minister.%20Over%20the%20last%2010%20years%2C%20people%20have%20seen%20this%20model%20of%20governance%20and%20thus%20have%20voted%20him%20to%20power%20for%20a%20third%20term%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prime%20minister%20was%20addressing%20a%20packed%20Nassau%20Veterans%20Coliseum%20with%20more%20than%2013%2C000%20Indian%20Americans.%20While%20the%20majority%20of%20them%20were%20from%20the%20New%20York%20and%20New%20Jersey%20area%2C%20Indian%20Americans%20came%20in%20from%2040%20States%2C%20organisers%20said.%20Sixty%20charter%20buses%20were%20used%20for%20transportation%20purposes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApplauding%20the%20role%20of%20Indian%20Americans%20in%20strengthening%20the%20relationship%20between%20India%20and%20the%20US%2C%20he%20called%20them%20as%20India's%20brand%20ambassadors.%20Referring%20to%20a%20Sanskrit%20shloka%20that%20%26quot%3Bit%20is%20those%20who%20make%20sacrifices%20reap%20benefits%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20said%20wherever%20the%20Indian%20diaspora%20lives%2C%20they%20contribute%20to%20the%20societal%20and%20national%20development%20in%20every%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20remarks%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20touched%20upon%20the%20celebration%20of%20democracy%20across%20the%20world%2C%20in%20particular%20in%20India%20and%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20the%20elections%20in%20India%20are%20over%2C%20it's%20under%20process%20in%20the%20United%20States.%20The%20elections%20that%20were%20just%20held%20in%20India%20were%20the%20biggest%20elections%20so%20far%20in%20human%20history.%20When%20we%20see%20the%20scale%20of%20India's%20democracy%2C%20we%20are%20even%20more%20proud%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20applauded%20the%20role%20of%20Indian%20Americans%20in%20making%20the%20country%20and%20community%20proud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20yesterday%2C%20President%20Biden%20took%20me%20to%20his%20home%20in%20Delaware.%20His%20affection%2C%20his%20warmth%2C%20it%20was%20a%20moment%20that%20touched%20my%20heart.%20This%20respect%20is%20for%20the%20140%20billion%20Indians.%20This%20respect%20is%20for%20you%2C%20for%20your%20achievements%2C%20for%20the%20hundreds%20and%20thousands%20of%20Indians%20living%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20and%20called%20Indian%20Americans%20as%20India's%20brand%20ambassador.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20referred%20to%20the%20recently%20concluded%20T-20%20World%20Cup%20in%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%2C%20he%20said%2C%20is%20now%20aspiring%20to%20be%20the%20third%20largest%20economy%20of%20the%20world%20from%20the%20fifth%20position.%20%26quot%3BToday%2C%20people%20of%20India%2C%20he%20said%2C%20are%20full%20of%20self-confidence%2C%20they%20have%20resolve%20and%20determination%20to%20achieve%20their%20goal%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20development%20in%20India%20has%20now%20become%20a%20people's%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20Indian%20has%20confidence%20in%20India%2C%20its%20achievements.%20India%20today%20is%20a%20land%20of%20opportunities.%20It's%20no%20longer%20waiting%20for%20opportunities.%20It%20is%20now%20creating%20opportunities%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20in%20just%20a%20decade%20250%20million%20people%20have%20been%20lifted%20out%20of%20poverty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20was%20possible%20because%20we%20changed%20our%20old%20way%20of%20thinking.%20We%20changed%20our%20approach.%20We%20empowered%20the%20poor%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20Indian%20Americans.%20It%20is%20this%20new%20middle%20class%2C%20which%20is%20accelerating%20the%20development%20of%20India%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20entertaining%20cultural%20performance%20was%20the%20main%20highlight%20of%20the%20event%20before%20the%20prime%20minister%20arrived.%20The%20Echoes%20of%20India%20-%20A%20Journey%20Through%20Art%20and%20Tradition%2C%20showcased%20382%20nationally%20and%20internationally%20known%20artists.%20Prominent%20among%20them%20including%20Grammy%20award%20nominee%20Chandrika%20Tandon%2C%20STAR%20Voice%20of%20India%20winner%20and%20superstar%20Aishwarya%20Majumdar%2C%20Instagram's%20Dancing%20Dad%20Ricky%20Pond%2C%20and%20singing%20sensation%20Rex%20DSouuza%2C%20in%20a%20seamless%20experience%20of%20India's%20cultural%20diversity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20unique%20performances%20by%20117%20artists%2C%20impressing%20and%20entertaining%20attendees%20as%20they%20enter%20the%20coliseum.%20Organisers%20said%20more%20than%2030%20classical%2C%20folk%2C%20modern%20and%20fusion%20performances%20will%20pay%20homage%20to%20the%20rich%20and%20diverse%20cultures%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727028060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fpc43k25_pm-modi-ani_625x300_22_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-us-visit-have-very-ambitious-goals-to-achieve-in-3rd-term-pm-modi-in-new-york-6626185%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20Sunday%20said%20that%20he%20h