iginID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc30lmpgvvvqo%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20will%20bring%20the%20Kenyan%20contingent%20helping%20Haitian%20police%20fight%20gangs%20up%20to%201%2C000.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A47%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc30lmpgvvvqo%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc30lmpgvvvqo.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc30lmpgvvvqo.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM%20To%20Address%20Huge%20Gathering%20Of%20Indian%20Community%20In%20US%20Today%3A%2010%20Points%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPM%20Modi%20has%20already%20met%20some%20members%20of%20the%20Indian%20diaspora.%20After%20he%20arrived%20at%20Hotel%20Lotte%20Palace%20in%20New%20York%2C%20the%20diaspora%20members%20greeted%20with%20a%20dance%20performance%20to%20an%20Indian%20folk%20song%2C%20and%20chanted%20%26quot%3BModi!%20Modi!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BHe%20has%20brought%20the%20golden%20age%20of%20India%20back.%20Modi%20ji%20is%20great...%20This%20is%20a%20historical%20moment%20for%20us%20to%20cherish%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20diaspora%20member%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAn%20Indian%20community%20member%20whose%20painting%20PM%20Modi%20had%20signed%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20met%20the%20PM%20today.%20It%20felt%20really%20good.%20The%20moment%20he%20saw%20my%20painting%2C%20he%20asked%20me%20where%20I%20come%20from.%20I%20told%20him%20I%20come%20from%20the%20Mithila%20region.%20The%20painting%20is%20based%20on%20the%20theme%20of%20Vasudhaiva%20Kutumbakam%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPM%20Modi%20yesterday%20had%20three%20separate%20bilateral%20meetings%20with%20Australian%20Prime%20Minister%20Anthony%20Albanese%2C%20Japanese%20Prime%20Minister%20Fumio%20Kishida%20and%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAt%20the%20Quad%20Leadership%20Summit%20later%20and%20others%20associated%20with%20it%2C%20PM%20Modi%20underlined%20India's%20approach%20of%20cooperation%2C%20contact%2C%20and%20engagement%20for%20growth%20with%20a%20variety%20of%20partners%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%2C%20Foreign%20Secretary%20Vikram%20Misri%20told%20reporters%20in%20New%20York.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWith%20the%20US%2C%20a%20special%20feature%20of%20the%20bilateral%20meeting%20was%20the%20return%20of%20297%20antiquities%20to%20India%2C%20a%20few%20of%20which%20were%20on%20display%20at%20Mr%20Biden's%20home%20during%20the%20bilateral%20meeting.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BIn%20fact%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20today%20referred%20to%20the%20Quad%20in%20a%20very%2C%20very%20evocative%20way.%20He%20called%20it%20quick%20unified%20assistance%20delivery%20(QUAD).%20The%20other%20members%20of%20the%20Quad%20said%20they%20finally%20understood%20what%20Quad%20signified%20and%20stood%20for%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Misri%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPM%20Modi%20also%20mentioned%20that%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20world%20is%20ridden%20with%20tensions%20and%20conflicts%2C%20the%20coming%20together%20of%20these%20four%20Quad%20partners%20with%20shared%20democratic%20values%20is%20important%20for%20humanity.%20He%20said%20the%20Quad%20was%20here%20to%20stay%2C%20to%20assist%2C%20to%20partner%20and%20to%20complement%20the%20efforts%20of%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20countries.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAmong%20the%20major%20announcements%20from%20the%20summit%20was%20the%20Quad%20Cancer%20Moonshot%2C%20which%20is%20a%20groundbreaking%20partnership%20to%20address%20the%20challenges%20posed%20by%20cancer%20and%20in%20this%20particular%20instance%20cervical%20cancer.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThere%20was%20discussion%20on%20many%20regional%20and%20global%20issues%2C%20and%20among%20them%20the%20need%20for%20the%20reform%20of%20the%20multilateral%20system%20of%20governance%2C%20including%20the%20United%20Nations%20Security%20C