ary%22%3A%22Kerala-based%20Beena%20Tom%20uses%20her%20cooking%20skills%20to%20make%20a%20variety%20of%20dishes%20from%20flowers%20and%20fruits%20available%20in%20her%20backyard%20%E2%80%93%20from%20coconut%2C%20arecanut%2C%20mangoes%2C%20guavas%2C%20to%20butterfly%20peas.%20Her%20passion%20led%20her%20to%20establish%20a%20thriving%20enterprise%20%E2%80%98Bees%20of%20Beena%E2%80%99%2C%20where%20she%20sells%20homemade%20jams%2C%20pickles%2C%20squash%2C%20juices%2C%20chips%2C%20and%20honey.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F366432%2Fhomemade-food-pickles-jams-in-kerala-homemaker-runs-business-organic-garden-bees-of-beena%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Battery%20Smart%3A%20Startup%20Does%201%20Lakh%20Electric%20Vehicle%20Battery%20Swaps%20Daily%3B%20Earns%2063%20Cr%20in%20Revenue%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBattery%20Smart%20%E2%80%94%20a%20market%20leader%20in%20facilitating%20battery%20swapping%20for%20two%20and%20three-wheeler%20electric%20vehicles%20(EVs)%20in%20India%20%E2%80%94%20reached%20a%20significant%20landmark%20last%20month.%20On%207%20August%2C%20the%20Delhi-based%20venture%20founded%20by%20IIT%20Kanpur%20graduates%20Pulkit%20Khurana%20and%20Siddharth%20Sikka%20announced%20that%20it%20had%20surpassed%20one%20lakh%20daily%20swaps%20on%20its%20network%20of%20over%2055%2C000%20drivers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20launch%20of%20its%20first%20swap%20station%20in%20Janakpuri%2C%20New%20Delhi%2C%20in%20June%202020%2C%20Battery%20Smart%20has%20rapidly%20expanded%20its%20network.%20With%201%2C200%20stations%20now%20spread%20across%20more%20than%2035%20cities%20in%20India%2C%20the%20Delhi-based%20electric%20mobility%20venture%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20leading%20player%20in%20the%20battery%20swapping%20sector%2C%20surpassing%2045%20million%20cumulative%20swaps%20to%20date%2C%20they%20claim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFounded%20in%202019%2C%20the%20objective%20of%20establishing%20Battery%20Smart%20was%20to%20make%20%E2%80%9CEV%20adoption%20simple%2C%20economical%20and%20accessible%20through%20a%20unique%20partner-led%20model%E2%80%9D%2C%20says%20Siddharth.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20battery%20swapping%20technology%20does%20for%20the%20electric%20mobility%20sector%20in%20India%20is%20address%20anxieties%20over%20the%20cost%20of%20EVs%20(since%20batteries%20make%20up%20as%20much%20as%2040%25%20of%20the%20production%20cost%20of%20a%20typical%20EV)%2C%20lack%20of%20adequate%20charging%20infrastructure%2C%20and%20the%20time%20taken%20to%20charge%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20context%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F279874%2Felectric-vehicles-sustainable-india-battery-reuse-recycling-renewable-energy-ev%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ee-mobility%20sector%3C%2Fa%3E%20dominated%20by%20two%20and%20three-wheelers%20that%20are%20primarily%20deployed%20for%20public%20transit%2C%20freight%20transport%2C%20and%20last-mile%20delivery%2Fconnectivity%2C%20battery-swapping%20technology%20makes%20more%20sense.%20With%20smaller%20vehicles%20comes%20a%20requirement%20for%20batteries%20that%20are%20lighter%20to%20carry%2C%20and%20therefore%20swap.%20Also%2C%20drivers%20of%20these%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20wait%20for%20a%20few%20hours%20to%20charge%20their%20vehicles%20and%20can%20instead%20swap%20their%20old%20batteries%20for%20charged%20ones%20in%20a%20few%20minutes.%20These%20features%20are%20especially%20useful%20for%20fleet%20operators%2C%20last-mile%20delivery%20persons%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Pulkit%20Khurana%2C%20co-founder%2C%20discusses%20his%20venture%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthekredible.com%2Fblogs%2Fbattery-smart-recorded-a-7-4x-