0rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F276266%2Fdr-anil-rajvanshi-wins-padma-shri-invents-electric-rickshaw-alcohol-stove%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eelectric%20rickshaws%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20India%20were%20powered%20by%20lead-acid%20batteries%2C%20serving%20nearly%2070%20million%20people%20for%20first%20and%20last-mile%20commutes.%20We%20recognised%20that%20high%20upfront%20costs%20were%20a%20significant%20barrier%20to%20adopting%20electric%20vehicles%20in%20a%20cost-conscious%20market%20like%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Pulkit%2C%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLead%20acid%20batteries%20require%20replacement%20every%20six%20months%2C%20making%20it%20a%20recurring%20capital%20expenditure%20problem%20for%20drivers.%20Moreover%2C%20drivers%20often%20spend%2010%20to%2012%20hours%20every%20night%20charging%20their%20batteries%20and%20another%203%20to%204%20hours%20to%20top%20it%20up%20during%20the%20day.%20Our%20goal%20was%20to%20upgrade%20the%20existing%20solution%20with%20better%20technology.%20Battery%20swapping%20emerged%20as%20the%20solution%2C%20as%20it%20eliminates%20the%20need%20for%20end%20users%20to%20own%20the%20battery%2C%20reducing%20upfront%20costs%20by%20as%20much%20as%2040%25%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20multiple%20ventures%20at%20the%20time%20that%20decided%20to%20get%20into%20the%20business%20of%20manufacturing%20EVs%20and%20chargers%2C%20Pulkit%20and%20Siddharth%20ventured%20into%20battery-swapping%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlthough%20manufacturing%20chargers%20and%20vehicles%20is%20an%20exciting%20field%2C%20we%20chose%20to%20focus%20on%20addressing%20key%20challenges%20such%20as%20range%20anxiety%2C%20charging%20downtime%2C%20and%20high%20costs.%20By%20partnering%20with%20over%20ten%20leading%20OEMs%20(original%20equipment%20manufacturers)%20working%20on%20battery%20development%20and%20manufacturing%2C%20we%20can%20stay%20ahead%20of%20the%20curve%20with%20changing%20technology.%20We%20always%20have%20the%20option%20to%20evaluate%20and%20choose%20from%20the%20best%20battery%20technology%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FBattery-Smart-Swapping-Station-14-1726583256.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22EV%20battery%20swapping%20technology%20works%20better%20than%20straight%20charging%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FBattery-Smart-Swapping-Station-14-1726583256.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FBattery-Smart-Swapping-Station-14-1726583256-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FBattery-Smart-Swapping-Station-14-1726583256-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FBattery-Smart-Swapping-Station-14-1726583256-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FBattery-Smart-Swapping-Station-14-1726583256-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-366328%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAt%20a%20Battery%20Smart%20Swap%20Station%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20do%20Battery%20Smart%E2%80%99s%20swapping%20stations%20operate%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Pulkit%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20use%20interoperable%20batteries%20for%20electric%20two%20and%20three-wheelers%2C%20allowing%20users%20to%20easily%20locate%20the%20nearest%20swapping%20station%20via%20the%20Battery%20Smart%20app.%20Our%20goal%20at%20Battery%20Smart%20is%20to%20build%20a%20dense%20network%20of%20swap%20stations%20by%20ensuring%20EV%20users%20are%20within%20a%20one-kilometre%20radius%20of%20a%20station%20with%20zero%20wait%20time.%20At%20the%20station%2C%20EV%20users%20on%20the%20Battery%20Smart%20network%20can%20quickly%20exchange%20their%20depleted%20battery%20for%20a%20fully%20charged%20one%20in%20under%20two%20minutes%2C%20and%20conveniently%20pay%20for%20each%20battery%20swap%20directly%20through%20the%20app.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUsing%20a%20battery-as-a-service%20model%2C%20we%20are%20making%20EV%20ownership%20more%20accessible%20and%20affordable.%20Our%20partner-led%20approach%20enables%20us%20to%20leverage%20existing%20infrastructure%20by%20partnering%20with%20small%20businesses%20and%20corner%20shops%20to%20rapidly%20expand%20our%20network%20and%20help%20boost%20their%20incomes.%20This%20has%20enabled%20us%20to%20expand%20our%20network%20to%20Tier%201%2C%202%2C%20and%203%20regions%20in%20India%2C%20where%20charging%20infrastructure%20is%20limited%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20their%20batteries%20are%20interoperable%2C%20Battery%20Smart%20claims%20to%20serve%20over%20200%20vehicle%20models%20with%20a%20single%20type%20of%20battery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20idea%20was%20to%20ensure%20that%20new%20users%20have%20a%20smooth%20transition%20from%20their%20internal%20combustion%20engine%20(ICE)%20vehicles%20to%20EVs.%20Battery%20swapping%20allows%20them%20to%20mimic%20the%20refuelling%20experience%2C%20by%20replacing%20the%20depleted%20battery%20with%20a%20fully%20charged%20battery%20in%20under%20two%20minutes.%20This%20ensures%20that%20the%20adoption%20of%20electric%20mobility%20is%20simple%20and%20efficient%2C%20leading%20to%20greater%20savings%20in%20time%2C%20covering%20longer%20distances%2C%20and%20increasing%20incomes%2C%E2%80%9D%20notes%20Pulkit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20single%20swap%20would%20cost%20users%20between%20Rs%20100%20and%20Rs%20150%2C%20and%20it%20offers%20a%20range%20of%20over%2060%20km%2C%20claims%20Siddharth.%20EV%20users%20can%20also%20opt%20for%20various%20subscription%20plans%20that%20suit%20their%20needs.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20vehicles%20have%20smart%20meters%2C%20which%20indicate%20to%20the%20users%20when%20to%20swap%2C%20and%20the%20rest%20%E2%80%94%20from%20locating%20the%20nearest%20swap%20station%20to%20payment%20%E2%80%94%20can%20be%20done%20on%20the%20Battery%20Smart%20app%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20the%20batteries%20they%20deploy%2C%20Pulkit%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20lithium-ion%20batteries%20we%20use%20are%20smart%20and%20interoperable%2C%20making%20them%20compatible%20with%20electric%20three%20and%20two-wheelers.%20These%20batteries%20are%20produced%20by%20different%20battery%20manufacturers%20but%20are%20identical%20in%20specifications%20and%20dimensions.%20This%20means%20that%20from%20a%20customer%E2%80%99s%20perspective%2C%20the%20same%20model%20of%20batteries%20is%20being%20swapped.%20We%20source%20our%20batteries%20from%20over%2010%20Lithium-ion%20battery%20OEMs%20in%20India%20based%20on%20their%20recent%20track%20record%20to%20ensure%20quality%20and%20reliability.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20how%20much%20does%20it%20cost%20to%20set%20up%20one%20battery%20swapping%20station%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20mentioned%2C%20we%20have%20a%20partner-led%20model%2C%20where%20we%20leverage%20the%20existing%20infrastructure%20and%20collaborate%20with%20local%20businesses%20to%20set%20up%20swap%20stations%20at%20a%20rapid%20pace%2C%20without%20the%20need%20for%20commissioning%20new%20real%20estate%20and%20can%20now%20open%20three%20to%20four%20stations%20every%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20claims%20Pulkit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20usually%20takes%20six%20weeks%20for%20a%20station%20to%20go%20live.%20Our%20partners%20only%20have%20to%20pay%20a%20licensing%20fee%2C%20while%20the%20rest%2C%20including%20all%20investments%20in%20chargers%20and%20batteries%2C%20is%20done%20by%20Battery%20Smart.%20Through%20this%20model%2C%20the%20partners%20are%20typically%20able%20to%20break%20even%20on%20their%20upfront%20fee%20within%20one%20year%20and%20get%20three%20years%20to%20operate%20under%20the%20standard%20agreement.%20Currently%2C%20through%20our%20partner%20network%20of%201%2C200%20swap%20stations%2C%20we%20do%20one%20lakh%20swaps%20a%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEnsuring%20compatibility%20with%20different%20EV%20models%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20battery-swapping%20venture%20catering%20to%20two%20and%20three-wheeler%20EVs%2C%20how%20does%20a%20venture%20like%20Battery%20Smart%20ensure%20such%20compatibility%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20we%20offer%20batteries%20through%20a%20Battery-as-a-Service%20model%2C%20we%20enable%20users%20to%20overcome%20common%20barriers%20to%20EV%20adoption.%20These%20batteries%20we%20use%20are%20interoperable%20and%20serve%20over%20200%20vehicle%20models%20with%20a%20single%20type%20of%20battery.%20So%2C%20while%20they%20may%20be%20produced%20by%20different%20OEMs%20the%20specifications%20and%20dimensions%20will%20be%20uniform%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Pulkit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20swappable%20batteries%20are%20around%202%20to%202.5%20kWh%20in%20capacity%2C%20and%20weigh%20about%2012%20to%2015%20kg.%20The%20smaller%20batteries%20result%20in%20lower%20weight%20of%20the%20electric%20two-wheeler%20and%20yield%20better%20energy%20efficiency%20and%20greater%20range%20on%20the%20available%20charge.%20An%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F333931%2Fbengaluru-startup-converts-petrol-two-wheeler-to-hybrid-electric%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eelectric%20two-wheeler%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20designed%20to%20run%20with%20one%20battery%2C%20whereas%20vehicles%2C%20such%20as%20e-rickshaws%20and%20e-autos%2C%20can%20be%20fitted%20with%20up%20to%20two%20such%20batteries%2C%20depending%20on%20their%20energy%20consumption%20and%20range%20requirements%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20goes%20on%20to%20state%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20partner%20OEMs%20provide%20warranty%2C%20performance%20and%20safety%20on%20their%20products%2C%20and%20while%20we%20conduct%20quality%20testing%20on%20them%20before%20rolling%20it%20out%20into%20the%20market.%20We%20invest%20significantly%20in%20developing%20safe%20Battery%20Management%20Software%20(BMS)%20technology%2C%20which%20is%20essential%20for%20effectively%20managing%20swappable%20batteries.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FBattery-Smart-Swapping-Station-13-1726583416.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22EV%20Battery%20Swapping%20Technology%20is%20the%20future%20of%20EV%20adoption%20in%20India%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FBattery-Smart-Swapping-Station-13-1726583416.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FBattery-Smart-Swapping-Station-13-1726583416-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FBattery-Smart-Swapping-Station-13-1726583416-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FBattery-Smart-Swapping-Station-13-1726583416-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FBattery-Smart-Swapping-Station-13-1726583416-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-366329%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98The%20swappable%20batteries%20are%20around%202%20to%202.5%20kWh%20in%20capacity%2C%20and%20weigh%20about%2012%20to%2015%20kg.%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%