20of%20critical%20parameters%2C%20such%20as%20voltage%2C%20temperature%2C%20and%20current.%20We%20also%20offer%2024%C3%977%20on-call%20support%20to%20our%20drivers%20and%20partners.%20In%20addition%2C%20we%20make%20sure%20that%20all%20station%20partners%20and%20drivers%20on%20board%20our%20network%20receive%20mandatory%20training%20programmes%20and%20refresher%20courses%20on%20proper%20battery%20management%2C%20storage%2C%20handling%2C%20and%20emergency%20response%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFuture%20of%20EV%20battery%20swapping%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.psmarketresearch.com%2Fmarket-analysis%2Findia-electric-vehicle-battery-swapping-market%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPrescient%20and%20Strategic%20Intelligence%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20market%20research%20venture%2C%20the%20Indian%20EV%20battery-swapping%20market%20stood%20at%20an%20estimated%20%2410.2%20million%20in%202022.%20This%20market%20is%20expected%20to%20reach%20%2461.57%20million%20by%202030%E2%80%93growth%20at%20a%20CAGR%20of%2025.20%25%20from%202022%20to%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20India%E2%80%99s%20last%20financial%20year%2C%20Indians%20bought%20over%2028%20million%20vehicles%2C%2012.5%25%20more%20than%20the%20previous%20year.%20Whether%20these%20consumers%20choose%20an%20internal%20combustion%20engine%20(ICE)%20vehicle%20over%20an%20electric%20vehicle%20and%20choose%20battery%20swapping%20over%20traditional%20charging%20methods%20largely%20comes%20down%20to%20cost.%20Additionally%2C%20battery%20charging%20requires%20high%20upfront%20expenditure%2C%20longer%20downtimes%2C%20parking%20and%20charging%20facilities%20(more%20area)%2C%20which%20can%20dissuade%20drivers%20from%20switching%20to%20electric%20alternatives%2C%20especially%20in%20Tier%201%20and%20Tier%202%20cities%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Pulkit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEVs%20currently%20account%20for%2020%25%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20last-mile%20delivery%20market%2C%20moving%20towards%20the%20Government%E2%80%99s%20target%20of%2030%25%20vehicle%20fleet%20electrification%20by%202030.%20On%20our%20roads%2C%20we%20can%20see%20that%20a%20significant%20number%20of%20fleet%20operators%20have%20moved%20to%20electric%20mobility.%20This%20is%20true%20for%20Tier%201%2C%20Tier%202%20and%20Tier%203%20cities.%20They%20are%20gaining%20from%20the%20zero-charging%20downtime%2C%20a%20unique%20advantage%20of%20battery%20swapping%20which%20helps%20drivers%20save%20time%20and%20stay%20on%20the%20road%20longer%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Images%20courtesy%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.batterysmart.in%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBattery%20Smart%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726585339000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FBattery-Smart-Swapping-Station-12-1726583051.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D366214%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Battery%20Smart%2C%20an%20EV%20battery%20tech%20startup%20founded%20by%20IIT-Kanpur%20graduates%20Pulkit%20Khurana%20and%20Siddharth%20Sikka%2C%20does%201%20lakh%20daily%20swaps%20on%20its%20network.%20With%20over%201%2C200%20stations%20across%20more%20than%2035%20cities%2C%20the%20startup%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20leading%20player%20in%20the%20EV%20battery-swapping%20sector.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Rinchen%20Norbu%20Wangchuk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A21%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F366214%2Fev-battery-smart-swapping-technology-startup-iit-kanpur-pulkit-khurana-siddharth-sikka%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Shreyovi%E2%80%99s%20Inspiring%20Journey%3A%20A%2010-YO%20Wildlife%20Pho