%20to%20capture%20animals%20in%20their%20natural%20habitat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20age%20of%20two%2C%20Shreyovi%E2%80%99s%20father%20let%20her%20touch%20his%20DSLR%20for%20the%20first%20time%20%E2%80%94%20a%20moment%20she%20still%20vividly%20recalls%20eight%20years%20later.%20She%20even%20remembers%20it%20happened%20during%20a%20trip%20to%20Ranthambore%20National%20Park.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFast%20forward%20seven%20years%2C%20and%20at%20nine%20years%20old%2C%20Shreyovi%20clicked%20a%20stunning%20photograph%20of%20two%20peahens%20at%20Keoladeo%20National%20Park.%20That%20photo%20went%20on%20to%20become%20the%20runner-up%20in%20the%2010%20Years%20and%20Under%20category%20of%20the%20Natural%20History%20Museum%2C%20London%E2%80%99s%2060th%20Wildlife%20Photographer%20of%20the%20Year%20award!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGrowing%20up%20amidst%20wildlife%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFaridabad%20residents%20Shivang%20and%20Kahini%20quickly%20noticed%20their%20daughter%20Shreyovi%E2%80%99s%20innate%20love%20for%20nature%20and%20wildlife%2C%20and%20they%20made%20it%20a%20point%20to%20take%20her%20outdoors%20whenever%20possible.%20With%20Shivang%20spending%20over%20300%20days%20a%20year%20in%20the%20field%2C%20it%20meant%20long%20stretches%20away%20from%20the%20family.%20Taking%20Shreyovi%20along%20on%20his%20wildlife%20expeditions%20became%20not%20only%20a%20way%20for%20her%20to%20connect%20with%20nature%20but%20also%20a%20special%20opportunity%20for%20father-daughter%20bonding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fshreyovi-1726580937.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shreyovi%20with%20her%20parents%20on%20a%20safari.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fshreyovi-1726580937.jpg%201280w%2C%2