0in%20nature.%20My%20children%20are%20fascinated%20by%20nature.%20Being%20on%20these%20trails%20or%20hikes%20promotes%20a%20connection%20with%20your%20children%2C%20yourself%20and%20nature.%20You%20learn%20with%20your%20children%20and%20it%20ignites%20in%20them%2C%20a%20quest%20to%20learn%20more.%20The%20most%20important%20thing%20is%20that%20children%20are%20self-engaged%20in%20nature%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Rhituparna%20is%20curating%20a%20Meghalaya%20trip%20with%20Nehal%20to%20encourage%20more%20parents%20to%20get%20their%20children%20out%20and%20discover%20the%20unique%20bonds%20that%20are%20formed%20among%20children%20and%20like-minded%20adults.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20time%2C%20Nehal%20expanded%20Heart%20%26amp%3B%20Soil%20to%20include%20trips%20outside%20Maharashtra%20like%20wildlife%20safaris.%20Currently%2C%20she%20is%20planning%20trips%20to%20Meghalaya%20and%20a%20wildlife%20safari%20to%20Pench%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20After%20running%20it%20alongside%20her%20full-time%20job%20for%20over%20a%20decade%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20focus%20on%20it%20full-time%20in%202024.%20What%20sets%20her%20trips%20apart%20is%20that%20children%20of%20all%20ages%20are%20welcome%2C%20making%20it%20easier%20for%20parents%20with%20toddlers%20to%20travel%20and%20enjoy%20nature%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20will%20bond%20as%20a%20family%20and%20understand%20each%20other%20better.%20Your%20children%20will%20not%20remember%20the%20gadgets%20or%20fancy%20gifts.%20They%20will%20remember%20these%20experiences%20that%20you%20gave%20them.%20It%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F349527%2Fnew-mothers-online-support-groups-postpartum-breastfeeding-formula-sleep-training-parenting%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edevelops%20their%20personality%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-67-1726490377.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Children%20being%20gleeful%2C%20having%20climbed%20a%20tree.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-67-1726490377.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-67-1726490377-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-67-1726490377-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-67-1726490377-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-67-1726490377-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-366076%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENature%20is%20one%20of%20the%20best%20teachers%2C%20says%20Nehal.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20parents%20with%20kids%20below%20three%2C%20she%20says%20that%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20of%20it%20as%20a%20challenge.%20%E2%80%9CJust%20go%20with%20the%20flow.%20You%20will%20experience%20the%20highs%20and%20lows%2C%20and%20misses%20and%20hits.%20Take%20everything%20with%20a%20pinch%20of%20salt%20as%20it%E2%80%99s%20all%20part%20of%20the%20journey%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOffering%20some%20words%20of%20advice%20to%20parents%20in%20an%20increasingly%20competitive%20world%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20take%20parenting%20as%20a%20pressure.%20Slow%20down.%20It%E2%80%99s%20okay%20to%20not%20be%20busy%20all%20the%20time.%20Let%20your%20children%20enjoy%20their%20childhood.%20There%E2%80%99s%20a%20world%20beyond%20gadgets%20and%20video%20games.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTravelli