2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Farmer%20Turns%20Cashew%20Crop%20Ruined%20By%20Rains%20into%20Sprouts%2C%20Pickles%20%26amp%3B%20More%3B%20Earns%20Rs%2025%20Lakh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20large%20produce%20of%20wet%2C%20harvested%20cashews%20was%20in%20front%20of%20Brijith%20Krishnan.%20The%20unseasonal%20rains%20in%20his%20hometown%20in%20Kerala%20had%20ruined%20the%20crop%20again.%20He%20knew%20this%20crop%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20fetch%20him%20any%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%20the%20same%20time%20in%202020%2C%20the%20mechanical%20engineering%20diploma%20holder%20also%20faced%20another%20challenging%20turn%20of%20events%20when%20he%20unexpectedly%20lost%20his%20job%20as%20a%20supervisor%20in%20an%20IT%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20this%2C%20the%20cashew%20farming%20industry%20%E2%80%93%20a%20traditional%20source%20of%20income%20for%20his%20family%20%E2%80%93%20was%20also%20on%20the%20decline.%20This%20double%20blow%20left%20him%20without%20a%20stable%20income%20source.%20He%20strived%20to%20permanently%20settle%20in%20his%20hometown%20and%20explore%20new%20avenues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20keen%20eye%20for%20innovation%20and%20a%20determination%20to%20make%20a%20meaningful%20impact%2C%20he%20observed%20the%20growing%20trend%20towards%20plant-based%20diets%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20vegan%20industry.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeveraging%20his%20mechanical%20engineering%20background%20and%20driven%20by%20a%20desire%20to%20create%20value%20in%20cashew%20farming%2C%20he%20delved%20into%20the%20unchartered%20territory%20of%20sprouting%20technology%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F17187%2Fyoung-innovator-created-one-kind-cashew-nut-grading-machine%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecashew%20nuts%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20he%20officially%20launched%20his%20venture%2C%20Eatery%20Malbarikas%2C%20which%20makes%20dishes%20from%20sprouted%20cas